    <item>
      <title>CVS 再次下调预期，启动 20 亿美元成本削减计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/cvs-slashes-outlook-again-launches-2-billion-cost-cutting-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于医疗费用持续飙升，CVS Health Corp. 连续第三个季度下调了 2024 年盈利预期，并宣布了削减成本的措施，以在几年内节省 20 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/cvs-slashes-outlook-again-launches-2-billion-cost-cutting-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 10:30:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰晤士水务公司在新的转型计划中面临更严格的监管</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/thames-water-agrees-to-early-special-measures-on-license-breach</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰晤士水务有限公司 (Thames Water Utilities Ltd.) 将很快受到英国监管机构的特别措施，因为这家陷入困境的公司正在竞相寻找新的投资者，以免资金耗尽。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/thames-water-agrees-to-early-special-measures-on-license-breach</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 07:05:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油价在复苏中上涨，交易员关注伊朗的报复行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-7</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着全球市场从近期的暴跌中复苏，且投资者仍然担心伊朗可能对以色列实施报复性打击，油价出现上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-7</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 23:29:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
